    ALLOWED_ATTR: ['href', 'title'],
  });

  return <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: sanitized }} />;
}
```

Notes:
- Prefer plain text unless HTML support is truly required.
- Never trust sanitization done only on the client if the HTML is reused elsewhere.
- Avoid rolling your own sanitizer with regex or string replacement.

